{
  "video_id": "6Waurx8e-1o",
  "title": "Leonard Susskind: My friend Richard Feynman",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16187.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18440.0,
      "text": "I decided when I was asked to do this"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18690.0,
      "end_time": 21767.0,
      "text": "that what I really wanted to talk about was my friend, Richard Feynman."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21791.0,
      "end_time": 25236.0,
      "text": "I was one of the fortunate few that really did get to know him"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 26670.0,
      "text": "and enjoyed his presence."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 30763.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m going to tell you about the Richard Feynman that I knew."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30787.0,
      "end_time": 33860.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure there are people here who could tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33110.0,
      "end_time": 34827.0,
      "text": "about the Richard Feynman they knew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34851.0,
      "end_time": 37376.0,
      "text": "and it would probably be a different Richard Feynman."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37400.0,
      "end_time": 39382.0,
      "text": "Richard Feynman was a very complex man."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39407.0,
      "end_time": 41382.0,
      "text": "He was a man of many, many parts."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41724.0,
      "end_time": 46470.0,
      "text": "He was, of course, foremost, a very, very, very great scientist."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47580.0,
      "end_time": 49236.0,
      "text": "He was an actor. You saw him act."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 52918.0,
      "text": "I also had the good fortune to be in those lectures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52942.0,
      "end_time": 54236.0,
      "text": "up in the balcony."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54796.0,
      "end_time": 56200.0,
      "text": "They were fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57145.0,
      "end_time": 58320.0,
      "text": "He was a philosopher."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58891.0,
      "end_time": 60610.0,
      "text": "He was a drum player."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60850.0,
      "end_time": 62440.0,
      "text": "He was a teacher par excellence."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63743.0,
      "end_time": 66400.0,
      "text": "Richard Feynman was also a showman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66424.0,
      "end_time": 67987.0,
      "text": "an enormous showman."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68110.0,
      "end_time": 70446.0,
      "text": "He was brash, irreverent."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71446.0,
      "end_time": 76236.0,
      "text": "He was full of macho, a kind of macho one-upmanship."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76715.0,
      "end_time": 80318.0,
      "text": "He loved intellectual battle."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80665.0,
      "end_time": 83314.0,
      "text": "He had a gargantuan ego."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84417.0,
      "end_time": 87893.0,
      "text": "But the man had, somehow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87917.0,
      "end_time": 90369.0,
      "text": "a lot of room at the bottom."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90393.0,
      "end_time": 95123.0,
      "text": "And what I mean by that is a lot of room, in my case --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95147.0,
      "end_time": 98236.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t speak for anybody else, but in my case --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 101539.0,
      "text": "a lot of room for another big ego."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101563.0,
      "end_time": 102953.0,
      "text": "Well, not as big as his,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102977.0,
      "end_time": 104857.0,
      "text": "but fairly big."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106150.0,
      "end_time": 108390.0,
      "text": "I always felt good with Dick Feynman."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108396.0,
      "end_time": 110370.0,
      "text": "It was always fun to be with him."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110846.0,
      "end_time": 112608.0,
      "text": "He always made me feel smart."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113130.0,
      "end_time": 115220.0,
      "text": "How can somebody like that make you feel smart?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115244.0,
      "end_time": 116410.0,
      "text": "Somehow he did."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 116434.0,
      "end_time": 118893.0,
      "text": "He made me feel smart. He made me feel he was smart."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118918.0,
      "end_time": 120869.0,
      "text": "He made me feel we were both smart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120893.0,
      "end_time": 124235.0,
      "text": "and the two of us could solve any problem whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125343.0,
      "end_time": 128351.0,
      "text": "And in fact, we did sometimes do physics together."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 128375.0,
      "end_time": 130419.0,
      "text": "We never published a paper together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130443.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131904.0,
      "text": "but we did have a lot of fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 134200.0,
      "end_time": 135236.0,
      "text": "He loved to win,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135939.0,
      "end_time": 138638.0,
      "text": "win these little macho games we would sometimes play."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 138663.0,
      "end_time": 141927.0,
      "text": "And he didn&#39;t only play them with me, but with all sorts of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 141951.0,
      "end_time": 143787.0,
      "text": "He would almost always win."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 143812.0,
      "end_time": 146875.0,
      "text": "But when he didn&#39;t win, when he lost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 146899.0,
      "end_time": 149536.0,
      "text": "he would laugh and seem to have just as much fun"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149560.0,
      "end_time": 150758.0,
      "text": "as if he had won."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151591.0,
      "end_time": 153739.0,
      "text": "I remember once he told me a story"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153763.0,
      "end_time": 155684.0,
      "text": "about a joke the students played on him."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156152.0,
      "end_time": 158689.0,
      "text": "I think it was for his birthday --"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 158713.0,
      "end_time": 160130.0,
      "text": "they took him for lunch"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160154.0,
      "end_time": 164772.0,
      "text": "to a sandwich place in Pasadena."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164796.0,
      "end_time": 166430.0,
      "text": "It may still exist; I don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166844.0,
      "end_time": 169426.0,
      "text": "Celebrity sandwiches was their thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169450.0,
      "end_time": 171790.0,
      "text": "You could get a Marilyn Monroe sandwich."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 171814.0,
      "end_time": 174114.0,
      "text": "You could get a Humphrey Bogart sandwich."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174633.0,
      "end_time": 176815.0,
      "text": "The students went there in advance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 176839.0,
      "end_time": 180237.0,
      "text": "and arranged that they&#39;d all order Feynman sandwiches."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180261.0,
      "end_time": 183248.0,
      "text": "One after another, they came in and ordered Feynman sandwiches."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 183272.0,
      "end_time": 184500.0,
      "text": "Feynman loved this story."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184524.0,
      "end_time": 188558.0,
      "text": "He told me this story, and he was really happy and laughing."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188582.0,
      "end_time": 191332.0,
      "text": "When he finished the story, I said to him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191356.0,
      "end_time": 194219.0,
      "text": "\"Dick, I wonder what would be the difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 194243.0,
      "end_time": 197236.0,
      "text": "between a Feynman sandwich and a Susskind sandwich.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 197751.0,
      "end_time": 199766.0,
      "text": "And without skipping a beat at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 199790.0,
      "end_time": 203310.0,
      "text": "he said, \"Well, they&#39;d be about the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 203560.0,
      "end_time": 206378.0,
      "text": "The only difference is a Susskind sandwich would have a lot more ham.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 206402.0,
      "end_time": 208870.0,
      "text": "\"Ham\" as in bad actor."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 208111.0,
      "end_time": 209635.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 209659.0,
      "end_time": 213690.0,
      "text": "Well, I happened to have been very quick that day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 213930.0,
      "end_time": 215236.0,
      "text": "and I said, \"Yeah, but a lot less baloney.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 218214.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 218238.0,
      "end_time": 219375.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 219399.0,
      "end_time": 222581.0,
      "text": "The truth of the matter"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 222605.0,
      "end_time": 226587.0,
      "text": "is that a Feynman sandwich had a load of ham,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226611.0,
      "end_time": 229390.0,
      "text": "but absolutely no baloney."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 230905.0,
      "end_time": 233178.0,
      "text": "What Feynman hated worse than anything else"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 233202.0,
      "end_time": 235204.0,
      "text": "was intellectual pretense --"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 235228.0,
      "end_time": 236457.0,
      "text": "phoniness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 236481.0,
      "end_time": 238908.0,
      "text": "false sophistication, jargon."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 240210.0,
      "end_time": 244478.0,
      "text": "I remember sometime during the mid-&#39;80s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 244502.0,
      "end_time": 248636.0,
      "text": "Dick and I and Sidney Coleman would meet a couple of times"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 248660.0,
      "end_time": 251825.0,
      "text": "up in San Francisco -- at some very rich guy&#39;s house --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 251849.0,
      "end_time": 253976.0,
      "text": "up in San Francisco for dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 254000.0,
      "end_time": 256236.0,
      "text": "And the last time the rich guy invited us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 258396.0,
      "text": "he also invited a couple of philosophers."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 258420.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260948.00000000003,
      "text": "These guys were philosophers of mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 260971.0,
      "end_time": 264335.0,
      "text": "Their specialty was the philosophy of consciousness."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 264360.0,
      "end_time": 267500.0,
      "text": "And they were full of all kinds of jargon."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 267740.0,
      "end_time": 269470.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m trying to remember the words --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 269494.0,
      "end_time": 273384.0,
      "text": "\"monism,\" \"dualism,\" categories all over the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 273408.0,
      "end_time": 276982.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know what those meant, neither did Dick or Sydney, for that matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 277600.0,
      "end_time": 278775.0,
      "text": "And what did we talk about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 278800.0,
      "end_time": 281375.0,
      "text": "Well, what do you talk about when you talk about minds?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 281399.0,
      "end_time": 283563.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s one obvious thing to talk about:"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 283587.0,
      "end_time": 285236.0,
      "text": "Can a machine become a mind?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 285838.0,
      "end_time": 287567.0,
      "text": "Can you build a machine"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 287591.0,
      "end_time": 290673.0,
      "text": "that thinks like a human being that is conscious?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 291101.0,
      "end_time": 294431.0,
      "text": "We sat around and talked about this -- we of course never resolved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 294455.0,
      "end_time": 296236.0,
      "text": "But the trouble with the philosophers"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 298236.0,
      "text": "is that they were philosophizing"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300604.0,
      "text": "when they should have been science-ophizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 301480.0,
      "end_time": 303388.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a scientific question, after all."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 303412.0,
      "end_time": 306318.0,
      "text": "And this was a very, very dangerous thing to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 306343.0,
      "end_time": 307772.0,
      "text": "around Dick Feynman."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 307796.0,
      "end_time": 309280.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 310538.0,
      "end_time": 313733.0,
      "text": "Feynman let them have it -- both barrels, right between the eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 313757.0,
      "end_time": 316828.0,
      "text": "It was brutal; it was funny -- ooh, it was funny."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 316852.0,
      "end_time": 318565.0,
      "text": "But it was really brutal."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 318589.0,
      "end_time": 320539.0,
      "text": "He really popped their balloon."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 321325.0,
      "end_time": 324825.0,
      "text": "But the amazing thing was -- Feynman had to leave a little early;"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 324849.0,
      "end_time": 327950.0,
      "text": "he wasn&#39;t feeling too well, so he left a little bit early."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 327975.0,
      "end_time": 330869.0,
      "text": "And Sidney and I were left there with the two philosophers."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 330893.0,
      "end_time": 333883.0,
      "text": "And the amazing thing is these guys were flying."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 333907.0,
      "end_time": 335722.0,
      "text": "They were so happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 336880.0,
      "end_time": 338342.0,
      "text": "They had met the great man;"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 338366.0,
      "end_time": 340794.0,
      "text": "they had been instructed by the great man;"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 340818.0,
      "end_time": 342758.0,
      "text": "they had an enormous amount of fun"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 342783.0,
      "end_time": 344968.0,
      "text": "having their faces shoved in the mud ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 346135.0,
      "end_time": 348594.0,
      "text": "And it was something special."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 348618.0,
      "end_time": 352700.0,
      "text": "I realized there was something just extraordinary about Feynman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 352310.0,
      "end_time": 355845.0,
      "text": "even when he did what he did."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 358674.0,
      "end_time": 361347.0,
      "text": "Dick -- he was my friend; I did call him Dick --"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 361372.0,
      "end_time": 364580.0,
      "text": "Dick and I had a little bit of a rapport."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 364820.0,
      "end_time": 366956.0,
      "text": "I think it may have been a special rapport that he and I had."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 366980.0,
      "end_time": 369603.0,
      "text": "We liked each other; we liked the same kind of things."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 369627.0,
      "end_time": 373110.0,
      "text": "I also like the intellectual macho games."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 373538.0,
      "end_time": 375618.0,
      "text": "Sometimes I would win, mostly he would win,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 375642.0,
      "end_time": 377236.0,
      "text": "but we both enjoyed them."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 379650.0,
      "text": "And Dick became convinced at some point"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 379674.0,
      "end_time": 383882.0,
      "text": "that he and I had some kind of similarity of personality."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 384486.0,
      "end_time": 385940.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think he was right."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 385964.0,
      "end_time": 388183.0,
      "text": "I think the only point of similarity between us"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 388207.0,
      "end_time": 390405.0,
      "text": "is we both like to talk about ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 390429.0,
      "end_time": 393270.0,
      "text": "But he was convinced of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 393294.0,
      "end_time": 396347.0,
      "text": "And the man was incredibly curious."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 396372.0,
      "end_time": 400460.0,
      "text": "And he wanted to understand what it was and why it was"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 400700.0,
      "end_time": 402897.0,
      "text": "that there was this funny connection."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 403634.0,
      "end_time": 405318.0,
      "text": "And one day, we were walking."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 405342.0,
      "end_time": 407168.0,
      "text": "We were in France, in Les Houches."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 407192.0,
      "end_time": 410816.0,
      "text": "We were up in the mountains, 1976."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 410840.0,
      "end_time": 415970.0,
      "text": "And Feynman said to me, \"Leonardo ...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 415122.0,
      "end_time": 418157.0,
      "text": "The reason he called me \"Leonardo\" is because we were in Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 418181.0,
      "end_time": 419832.0,
      "text": "and he was practicing his French."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 419856.0,
      "end_time": 421976.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 422000.0,
      "end_time": 425223.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"Leonardo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 425247.0,
      "end_time": 429236.0,
      "text": "were you closer to your mother or your father when you were a kid?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 432236.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Well, my real hero was my father."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 433317.0,
      "end_time": 435468.0,
      "text": "He was a working man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 435492.0,
      "end_time": 437145.0,
      "text": "had a fifth-grade education."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 437635.0,
      "end_time": 440459.0,
      "text": "He was a master mechanic, and he taught me how to use tools."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 440483.0,
      "end_time": 444451.0,
      "text": "He taught me all sorts of things about mechanical things."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 444475.0,
      "end_time": 446506.0,
      "text": "He even taught me the Pythagorean theorem."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 446530.0,
      "end_time": 448482.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t call it the hypotenuse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 448507.0,
      "end_time": 450575.0,
      "text": "he called it the shortcut distance.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 451115.0,
      "end_time": 453892.0,
      "text": "And Feynman&#39;s eyes just opened up."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 453916.0,
      "end_time": 455509.0,
      "text": "He went off like a lightbulb."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 456271.0,
      "end_time": 458352.0,
      "text": "And he said that he had had"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 458376.0,
      "end_time": 461534.0,
      "text": "basically exactly the same relationship with his father."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 462130.0,
      "end_time": 465550.0,
      "text": "In fact, he had been convinced at one time"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 465574.0,
      "end_time": 469385.0,
      "text": "that to be a good physicist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 469409.0,
      "end_time": 472742.0,
      "text": "it was very important to have had that kind of relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 472766.0,
      "end_time": 473922.0,
      "text": "with your father."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 473946.0,
      "end_time": 476952.0,
      "text": "I apologize for the sexist conversation here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 476976.0,
      "end_time": 478836.0,
      "text": "but this is the way it really happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 478860.0,
      "end_time": 482657.0,
      "text": "He said he had been absolutely convinced that this was necessary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 482681.0,
      "end_time": 486320.0,
      "text": "a necessary part of the growing up of a young physicist."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 486915.0,
      "end_time": 490480.0,
      "text": "Being Dick, he, of course, wanted to check this."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 490720.0,
      "end_time": 492348.0,
      "text": "He wanted to go out and do an experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 492372.0,
      "end_time": 493388.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 493412.0,
      "end_time": 494563.0,
      "text": "Well, he did."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 494588.0,
      "end_time": 496246.0,
      "text": "He went out and did an experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 496270.0,
      "end_time": 499185.0,
      "text": "He asked all his friends that he thought were good physicists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 499209.0,
      "end_time": 501554.0,
      "text": "\"Was it your mom or your pop that influenced you?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 501578.0,
      "end_time": 503541.0,
      "text": "They were all men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 503565.0,
      "end_time": 506195.0,
      "text": "and to a man, every single one of them said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 506219.0,
      "end_time": 507443.0,
      "text": "\"My mother.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 507467.0,
      "end_time": 510534.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 510558.0,
      "end_time": 514558.0,
      "text": "There went that theory, down the trash can of history."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 514582.0,
      "end_time": 515686.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 515710.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518512.00000000006,
      "text": "But he was very excited that he had finally met somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 518534.99999999994,
      "end_time": 522130.99999999994,
      "text": "who had the same experience with his father"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 522155.0,
      "end_time": 523590.0,
      "text": "as he had with his father."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 523615.0,
      "end_time": 527740.0,
      "text": "And for some time, he was convinced this was the reason we got along so well."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 527764.0,
      "end_time": 529401.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know. Maybe. Who knows?"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 529860.0,
      "end_time": 533652.0,
      "text": "But let me tell you a little bit about Feynman the physicist."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 535882.0,
      "end_time": 539835.0,
      "text": "Feynman&#39;s style -- no, \"style\" is not the right word."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 539860.0,
      "end_time": 542705.0,
      "text": "\"Style\" makes you think of the bow tie he might have worn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 542729.0,
      "end_time": 544300.0,
      "text": "or the suit he was wearing."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 544540.0,
      "end_time": 545973.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something much deeper than that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 545997.0,
      "end_time": 548680.0,
      "text": "but I can&#39;t think of another word for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 548920.0,
      "end_time": 553534.0,
      "text": "Feynman&#39;s scientific style was always to look for the simplest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 553558.0,
      "end_time": 557473.0,
      "text": "most elementary solution to a problem that was possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 557497.0,
      "end_time": 561210.0,
      "text": "If it wasn&#39;t possible, you had to use something fancier."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 561729.0,
      "end_time": 566301.0,
      "text": "No doubt, part of this was his great joy and pleasure"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 566325.0,
      "end_time": 569757.0,
      "text": "in showing people that he could think more simply than they could."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 570970.0,
      "end_time": 573256.0,
      "text": "But he also deeply believed, he truly believed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 573280.0,
      "end_time": 575520.0,
      "text": "that if you couldn&#39;t explain something simply,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 575544.0,
      "end_time": 577740.0,
      "text": "you didn&#39;t understand it."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 578400.0,
      "end_time": 581653.0,
      "text": "In the 1950s, people were trying to figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 581677.0,
      "end_time": 583653.0,
      "text": "how superfluid helium worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 584573.0,
      "end_time": 585749.0,
      "text": "There was a theory."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 585773.0,
      "end_time": 588184.0,
      "text": "It was due to a Russian mathematical physicist."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 588208.0,
      "end_time": 589617.0,
      "text": "It was a complicated theory;"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 589642.0,
      "end_time": 591753.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll tell you what it was soon enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 591777.0,
      "end_time": 593625.0,
      "text": "It was a terribly complicated theory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 593649.0,
      "end_time": 596486.0,
      "text": "full of very difficult integrals and formulas"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 596510.0,
      "end_time": 598335.0,
      "text": "and mathematics and so forth."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 598860.0,
      "end_time": 602970.0,
      "text": "And it sort of worked, but it didn&#39;t work very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 602121.0,
      "end_time": 603463.0,
      "text": "The only way it worked"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 603487.0,
      "end_time": 606706.0,
      "text": "is when the helium atoms were very, very far apart."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 606730.0,
      "end_time": 609443.0,
      "text": "And unfortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 609467.0,
      "end_time": 612625.0,
      "text": "the helium atoms in liquid helium are right on top of each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 612649.0,
      "end_time": 615990.0,
      "text": "Feynman decided, as a sort of amateur helium physicist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 616140.0,
      "end_time": 618264.0,
      "text": "that he would try to figure it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 618288.0,
      "end_time": 620692.0,
      "text": "He had an idea, a very clear idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 620716.0,
      "end_time": 622110.0,
      "text": "He would try to figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 622134.0,
      "end_time": 627210.0,
      "text": "what the quantum wave function of this huge number of atoms looked like."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 627234.0,
      "end_time": 628881.0,
      "text": "He would try to visualize it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 628905.0,
      "end_time": 631836.0,
      "text": "guided by a small number of simple principles."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 631860.0,
      "end_time": 634836.0,
      "text": "The small number of simple principles were very, very simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 634860.0,
      "end_time": 638237.0,
      "text": "The first one was that when helium atoms touch each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 638261.0,
      "end_time": 639569.0,
      "text": "they repel."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 639593.0,
      "end_time": 642991.0,
      "text": "The implication of that is that the wave function has to go to zero,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 643150.0,
      "end_time": 646100.0,
      "text": "it has to vanish when the helium atoms touch each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 646124.0,
      "end_time": 648433.0,
      "text": "The other fact is that in the ground state --"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 648457.0,
      "end_time": 651194.0,
      "text": "the lowest energy state of a quantum system --"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 651218.0,
      "end_time": 654488.0,
      "text": "the wave function is always very smooth;"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 654513.0,
      "end_time": 656608.0,
      "text": "it has the minimum number of wiggles."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 656632.0,
      "end_time": 658160.0,
      "text": "So he sat down --"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 658184.0,
      "end_time": 660454.0,
      "text": "and I imagine he had nothing more"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 660479.0,
      "end_time": 662892.0,
      "text": "than a simple piece of paper and a pencil --"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 662916.0,
      "end_time": 665156.0,
      "text": "and he tried to write down, and did write down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 665180.0,
      "end_time": 667474.0,
      "text": "the simplest function that he could think of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 667499.0,
      "end_time": 669476.0,
      "text": "which had the boundary conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 669500.0,
      "end_time": 671964.0,
      "text": "that the wave function vanish when things touch"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 671988.0,
      "end_time": 673701.0,
      "text": "and is smooth in between."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 674493.0,
      "end_time": 677232.0,
      "text": "He wrote down a simple thing -- so simple, in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 677256.0,
      "end_time": 680382.0,
      "text": "that I suspect a really smart high-school student"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 680407.0,
      "end_time": 681836.0,
      "text": "who didn&#39;t even have calculus"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 681860.0,
      "end_time": 683793.0,
      "text": "could understand what he wrote down."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 684337.0,
      "end_time": 687486.0,
      "text": "The thing was, that simple thing that he wrote down"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 687510.0,
      "end_time": 691510.0,
      "text": "explained everything that was known at the time about liquid helium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 691750.0,
      "end_time": 692348.0,
      "text": "and then some."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 692764.0,
      "end_time": 695741.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve always wondered whether the professionals --"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 695765.0,
      "end_time": 697826.0,
      "text": "the real professional helium physicists --"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 697850.0,
      "end_time": 700170.0,
      "text": "were just a little bit embarrassed by this."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 700422.0,
      "end_time": 703910.0,
      "text": "They had their super-powerful technique,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 703115.0,
      "end_time": 704891.0,
      "text": "and they couldn&#39;t do as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 704915.0,
      "end_time": 709410.0,
      "text": "Incidentally, I&#39;ll tell you what that super-powerful technique was."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 709660.0,
      "end_time": 711615.0,
      "text": "It was the technique of Feynman diagrams."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 711639.0,
      "end_time": 713496.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 713520.0,
      "end_time": 716274.0,
      "text": "He did it again in 1968."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 716781.0,
      "end_time": 721766.0,
      "text": "In 1968, in my own university -- I wasn&#39;t there at the time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 721791.0,
      "end_time": 724363.0,
      "text": "they were exploring the structure of the proton."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 724757.0,
      "end_time": 728372.0,
      "text": "The proton is obviously made of a whole bunch of little particles;"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 728397.0,
      "end_time": 730337.0,
      "text": "this was more or less known."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 730782.0,
      "end_time": 734118.0,
      "text": "And the way to analyze it was, of course, Feynman diagrams."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 734142.0,
      "end_time": 736683.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what Feynman diagrams were constructed for --"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 736707.0,
      "end_time": 737976.0,
      "text": "to understand particles."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 738494.0,
      "end_time": 741106.0,
      "text": "The experiments that were going on were very simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 741130.0,
      "end_time": 742465.0,
      "text": "you simply take the proton,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 742489.0,
      "end_time": 745990.0,
      "text": "and you hit it really sharply with an electron."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 745123.0,
      "end_time": 747814.0,
      "text": "This was the thing the Feynman diagrams were for."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 748251.0,
      "end_time": 752314.0,
      "text": "The only problem was that Feynman diagrams are complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 752338.0,
      "end_time": 753877.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re difficult integrals."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 753902.0,
      "end_time": 757730.0,
      "text": "If you could do all of them, you would have a very precise theory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 757970.0,
      "end_time": 759674.0,
      "text": "but you couldn&#39;t -- they were just too complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 760573.0,
      "end_time": 762340.0,
      "text": "People were trying to do them."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 762580.0,
      "end_time": 764978.0,
      "text": "You could do a one-loop diagram. Don&#39;t worry about one loop."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 765200.0,
      "end_time": 768700.0,
      "text": "One loop, two loops -- maybe you could do a three-loop diagram,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 768310.0,
      "end_time": 770840.0,
      "text": "but beyond that, you couldn&#39;t do anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 770109.0,
      "end_time": 771753.0,
      "text": "Feynman said, \"Forget all of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 771777.0,
      "end_time": 773248.0,
      "text": "Just think of the proton"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 773272.0,
      "end_time": 777605.0,
      "text": "as an assemblage, a swarm, of little particles.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 777629.0,
      "end_time": 779280.0,
      "text": "He called them \"partons.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 779304.0,
      "end_time": 785700.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Just think of it as a swarm of partons moving real fast.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 785310.0,
      "end_time": 787117.0,
      "text": "Because they&#39;re moving real fast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 788256.0,
      "end_time": 792358.0,
      "text": "relativity says the internal motions go very slow."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 793810.0,
      "end_time": 794693.0,
      "text": "The electron hits it suddenly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 794717.0,
      "end_time": 798774.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s like taking a very sudden snapshot of the proton."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 799413.0,
      "end_time": 800568.0,
      "text": "What do you see?"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 800592.0,
      "end_time": 804626.0,
      "text": "You see a frozen bunch of partons."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 804650.0,
      "end_time": 805832.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t move,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 805856.0,
      "end_time": 808912.0,
      "text": "and because they don&#39;t move during the course of the experiment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 808936.0,
      "end_time": 811245.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t have to worry about how they&#39;re moving."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 811269.0,
      "end_time": 813875.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have to worry about the forces between them."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 813899.0,
      "end_time": 819880.0,
      "text": "You just get to think of it as a population of frozen partons.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 819574.0,
      "end_time": 823380.0,
      "text": "This was the key to analyzing these experiments."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 823620.0,
      "end_time": 825836.0,
      "text": "Extremely effective."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 826247.0,
      "end_time": 828748.0,
      "text": "Somebody said the word \"revolution\" is a bad word."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 828773.0,
      "end_time": 830914.0,
      "text": "I suppose it is, so I won&#39;t say \"revolution,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 830938.0,
      "end_time": 836439.0,
      "text": "but it certainly evolved very, very deeply our understanding of the proton,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 836464.0,
      "end_time": 838260.0,
      "text": "and of particles beyond that."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 838630.0,
      "end_time": 841248.0,
      "text": "Well, I had some more that I was going to tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 841272.0,
      "end_time": 842929.0,
      "text": "about my connection with Feynman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 842953.0,
      "end_time": 844127.0,
      "text": "what he was like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 844151.0,
      "end_time": 846454.0,
      "text": "but I see I have exactly half a minute."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 846479.0,
      "end_time": 850406.0,
      "text": "So I think I&#39;ll just finish up by saying:"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 850430.0,
      "end_time": 853226.0,
      "text": "I actually don&#39;t think Feynman would have liked this event."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 853250.0,
      "end_time": 857539.0,
      "text": "I think he would have said, \"I don&#39;t need this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 858142.0,
      "end_time": 859292.0,
      "text": "But ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 859316.0,
      "end_time": 860324.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 860348.0,
      "end_time": 861705.0,
      "text": "How should we honor Feynman?"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 861730.0,
      "end_time": 863412.0,
      "text": "How should we really honor Feynman?"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 863436.0,
      "end_time": 866580.0,
      "text": "I think the answer is we should honor Feynman"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 866604.0,
      "end_time": 870566.0,
      "text": "by getting as much baloney out of our own sandwiches"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 870590.0,
      "end_time": 871836.0,
      "text": "as we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 872201.0,
      "end_time": 873352.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 873376.0,
      "end_time": 876577.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}